      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented QA procedures and version control meets Gradation 1 requirements at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 was used under an institutional software QA plan. Version control, release notes, and regression test suite documentation were reviewed and confirmed adequate for MRL 2."
    },
    {
