      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experiments were conducted at 2–7 L/min and 1500–3500 RPM using porcine blood analog (glycerol-water, viscosity 3.5 cP at 37 °C). Boundary conditions in the CFD model were set to match measured values; deviations were within ±2% of nominal."
