      "rationale": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) values ranged from 0.0021 to 0.0087 mg/dL across the five operating points; measured values ranged from 0.0019 to 0.0091 mg/dL. Maximum relative error was 13.4%, satisfying the 20% criterion."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
